Set RIOTBASE path in the Makefile.

Apply riot_build.patch to RIOTBASE/. It disables -Wpedantic, -Werror
and few other warnings.

export BOARD=native && make CLIENT=1 (or make SERVER=1)
(Add DEBUG=1 for debug output)
This builds the client_riot/server_riot samples.

Setup a tap interface:
sudo ip tuntap add tap0 mode tap user ${USER}
sudo ip link set tap0 up

Run the application:
bin/native/ocf_app.elf tap0
